# Tropo grid: same-domain rewrite from the renderer's expected
# /src/tropo/data/grid.bin path to the Pages Function at
# /tropo/grid.bin (functions/tropo/grid.bin.js), which proxies the
# R2 bucket served at data.ionocast.org.  Same-domain so the
# rewrite actually proxies (cross-domain rewrites in _redirects
# fall through to the SPA fallback, not what we want).  Local dev
# still resolves /src/tropo/data/grid.bin to the file on disk.
/src/tropo/data/grid.bin           /tropo/grid.bin               200
